_sText:
gg_hexagon_k

Simple 6 sides mirrored gungame map, enjoy!

46 spawns
1 elevator
2 staircases

Note: Of course some of the "texture" textures are backwards, that's a common issue among every texture map. Plus, it saves me a few hours re-aligning the textures on the faces of the stairs/elevator.

Update: I plan on making a retextured version, so stay tuned.
